<D>__{it would be my pleasure.}
<C>__{escobar}
<D>__{good. very good. welcome, my friend. welcome to my country.}
<A>__{escobar moves over to embrace george. george returns it, and their hands come together. george can't help it. he reflexively looks at his hands. escobar understands.}
<C>__{escobar }
<D>__{the man in the garden. he was full of courage.}
<C>__{george}
<D>__{un sapo?}
<C>__{escobar}
<D>__{un rata no good. but he could have run, fled the country. gone to the policia. but then his wife, his children, his parents, his friends, many people would die.}
