<D>__{but, never mind. i am thinking we can do much together. this problem with diego, the stolen car, the jail, is very silly business. to release him from the carcel, it causes me much inconvenience. the fifty kilos could have been a big problem. and i don't like problems.}
<C>__{george}
<D>__{with all respect, padrino. diego is my partner. i do not do business without him.}
<A>__{escobar looks at him with a cold stare. but george doesn't flinch. his face reveals nothing. finally, a smile breaks across pablo's lips.}
